title: Looking for casual team URF
body: Hey guys I was just wondering if anyone wanted to join my duo buddy and I in some fun URF games or just any gamemode really (urf, norms, aram, custom etc) I just really prefer playing with premades rather than randoms. We don't use teamspeak but we do have skype if anyone is interested add me please :) This is just for fun it's nothing serious and we won't rage it you (I main mid and supp and my duo buddy mains jungle) IGN = Invictous Blade
